{"tid":383393,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"學Python用咩resources最好","createTime":"2017-09-01T12:29:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T16:07:32.000Z","uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a5435ca3a1e0b33c059aa9b1ba7db16077e046a3","tid":383393,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:29:28.000Z","msg":"對physics simulation, game programming, natural language processing, machine learning, deep learning, data science既python應用全部有興趣<br />\n網上啲resources真係太多太亂, 唔知用邊個入手好<br />\n利申淨係識基本syntax <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇起上黎簡單過java同c++太多, 好似咁易學咁搞到好撚hi想快啲學咗佢<br />\n同埋唔介意畀一次好似coursera上course咁49 USD去學 (不過唔使畀當然更好) <br />\nnewboston都睇緊, 不過好似唔夠全面咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e82e932a1934ccb2232da095fe12c3496e080f5","tid":383393,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:31:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.coursera.org/specializations/computer-fundamentals#faq-list\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coursera.org%2Fspecializations%2Fcomputer-fundamentals%23faq-list&d=Od297faog6gO%2BNk5sSXTT2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=63c5a2de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.coursera.org/specializations/computer-fundamentals#faq-list</a><br />\n呢個值唔值得讀?"},{"pid":"a95410e3fd43ae8f470a2685d7c10709a19d648e","tid":383393,"uid":75692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T13:12:50.000Z","msg":"學完揾D野黎寫下 睇下書<br />\n2-3個月 應該有D野睇下啦"},{"pid":"b63fc0a46c0ca10e9737d54cd83ed5ece9832b71","tid":383393,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T13:28:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學完揾D野黎寫下 睇下書<br />\n2-3個月 應該有D野睇下啦</blockquote><br />\n決定讀下上面嗰個coursera, 還掂有七日free trial睇下岩唔岩玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e922578b19e3da408502f57e49b86c5903fe1d","tid":383393,"uid":93141,"like":0,"disl