\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果個specialisation係用python<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 岩哂你<br />\n<br />\nMatlab始終太貴(冇licence好煩)，octave係unusable<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解octave unusable <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 太慢?"},{"pid":"e8cec97af13a43e0f0d0289823221e913a5c99f1","tid":383393,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T12:11:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>coursera Andrew Ng嗰 machine learning 都唔錯<br />\n不過係用Octave / Matlab</blockquote><br />\n我直接搵咗本introduction to machine learning in python - a guide for data scientists <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過andrew ng好似開咗一系列收費deep learning course <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果個specialisation係用python<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 岩哂你<br />\n<br />\nMatlab始終太貴(冇licence好煩)，octave係unusable<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解octave unusable <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 太慢?</blockquote><br />\n好慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前由Matlab轉過去用過一排，run machine learning真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"845c6ebf206497ade436454702523685308cbc83","tid":383393,"uid":4824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:49:46.000Z","msg":"巴打你最後選擇左係德國讀master 定cs degree？<br />\n你學緊python 應該都選擇左cs <br />\n係德國讀cs 係咪德文講解 英文寫program ？"},{"pid":"4370c5396daeeb3b8db2e3534155137e20273bbf","tid":383393,"uid":8632,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T19:08:33.000Z","msg":"如果由零開始<br />\n我覺得codecademy 好好<br />\n由頭到尾做一次啲練習<br />\n基本上要識嘅都有教<br />\n跟住去leetcode 做下練習<br />\n慢慢就會熟手<br />\nprogramming language 都係language<br />\n無所謂最好嘅textbook<br />\n上leetcode 睇啲5星星範文好過<br />\ndatacamp比較專門<br />\n可以擺喺codecademy 之後<br />\ncousera 睇咩course<br />\nandrew ng 個machine learning 好好<br />\n由淺入深<br />\n不過你預咗唔會一次明晒<br />\n同埋有心機有時間可以搵多啲唔同source<br />\n會<br />\n會易啲明<br />\n我自己就都係唔係好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n苦苦掙扎中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nNLP 可以睇下jurafsky 本書<br />\n不過成千頁 NLP wiki 咁滯<br />\n唔怕簡體字可以睇吳軍嘅數學之美<br />\n當故仔書睇<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ddb9df89a3d1ceb6db4e43c8c666c823f262aac","tid":383393,"uid":8632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T19:20:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.kdnuggets.com/2017/04/10-free-must-read-books-machine-learning-data-science.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kdnuggets.com%2F2017%2F04%2F10-free-must-read-books-machine-learning-data-science.html&d=Od297faog6gO%2BNk5sSXTT2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=22153870\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.kdnuggets.com/2017/04/10-free-must-read-books-machine-learning-data-science.html</a><br />\n呢堆書好撚hard core下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能要再補一補啲數底stat底先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/05/031820_850acf7e994c1e3f08a96bba5d4a899f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F05%2F031820_850acf7e994c1e3f08a96bba5d4a899f.jpg&h=c86d19f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有兩本喺手<br />\n左邊本花書係最新嘅deep learning 聖經<br />\n睇唔撚明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日攞去還咗去"},{"pid":"08dbaf0d363629a54b7460b945151773d2d305eb","tid":383393,"ui